         !text "Long ago, in times beyond remembrance,  "
         !text "Solon the Master Wizard and wearer of   "
         !text "the Secret Cloak lost the 13 Stars of   "
         !text "Power. The grasping Vileroth believed   "
         !text "the Stars to be the source of Solon's   "
         !text "expert wizardry. But unbeknownst to     "
         !text "Vileroth, it was the Secret Cloak that  "
         !text "controlled the Stars and protected the  "
         !text "wearer from their awesome powers. Unable"
         !text "to master the Stars, Vileroth was       "
         !text "undone.                                 "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "In his final days, as Vileroth's        "
         !text "strength slipped from him, he concealed "
         !text "the 13 Stars of Power within the Castle "
         !text "of Claymorgue...                        "
